title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Lockheed L-18 Lodestar - version 1.0
description:
In this video we will look at the Lockheed L-18 Lodestar which has been released today and is a converted FSX to MSFS aircraft. It is delivered with 9 liveries and is using the CJ-4 cockpit currently. Although the aircraft already can go airborne their is still a lot of work to do,

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/21948/lockheed-l-18-lodestar
